                "totalDuration": "4 mos",
                "employmentType": "Internship",
                "description": "As a dedicated Coach at Hawk Insight, I play a crucial role in guiding participants through every stage of developing their own projects. My responsibilities include:\n\nComprehensive Business Planning:\n\nCollaborate with participants to create all-encompassing plans necessary for building a business from scratch, including:\nBusiness Model Canvas (BMC): Designing a clear and strategic framework for the business model.\nOperational Plan: Outlining the day-to-day operations and processes to ensure smooth functioning.\nFinancial Plan: Developing detailed financial projections and budgeting to manage resources effectively.\nMarketing Plan: Crafting strategies to promote the business and reach the target audience.\nSkills Training and Development:\n\nProvide training on essential soft skills required for effective communication and project management.\nTeach presentation skills to help participants deliver compelling and impactful pitches.\nWorkshop Preparation and Delivery:\n\nDesign and facilitate workshops tailored to the specific needs of participants, focusing on practical application and collaborative learning.\nConduct interactive sessions to enhance participants' understanding and application of key concepts.\nProject Mentorship:\n\nOffer continuous support and mentorship throughout the project development phase, providing valuable feedback and guidance to refine ideas and achieve success.\nThrough these efforts, I aim to empower participants with the necessary tools and knowledge to build successful businesses and make a significant impact in their respective fields.",
